{"tid":110101,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人講下自己理想生活係點？","createTime":"2017-02-06T12:36:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T14:57:20.000Z","uid":62650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e9561df423e79505c5fb2812060bef61d9184a17","tid":110101,"uid":62650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T12:36:14.000Z","msg":"我先。<br />\n1. 有個電腦專業資格(係邊樣唔講）<br />\n2. 有錢到唔使做<br />\n3. 係外國生活 （獨立屋個隻）<br />\n4. 有個後生靚處女一齊生活(無結婚個隻）<br />\n5. 無聊時間唔中返香港探朋友<br />\n<br />\n其他基本唔講。"},{"pid":"0040860b27129b3e6ba2db9a6e1664fc8d00a7cb","tid":110101,"uid":4548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T12:42:37.000Z","msg":"每日有時間做運動 <br />\n每星期去行一至兩次山<br />\n每星期做一次義工<br />\n多啲同屋企人一齊買餸煮飯<br />\n每日瞓九個鐘 <br />\n有自己喜歡的工作 ，壓力較少<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab05bee39ece6fa30c6af18815ac71975ff31dba","tid":110101,"uid":80580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T12:43:48.000Z","msg":"日日番工搭的士"},{"pid":"979cc40001128ed8ab0ea6b69c0b3509a2d51c28","tid":110101,"uid":62650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T12:43:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每日有時間做運動 <br />\n每星期去行一至兩次山<br />\n每星期做一次義工<br />\n多啲同屋企人一齊買餸煮飯<br />\n每日瞓九個鐘 <br />\n有自己喜歡的工作 ，壓力較少<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔使返工一定大把時間"},{"pid":"7f339c0bf9fc878518322b9a72212f50392d5e5b","tid":110101,"uid":6142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T12:44:32.000Z","msg":"坐係度都有錢收<br />\n有個細粒女朋友，日日扑野<br />\n住大屋，一個月飛一次<br />\n買野食野唔使睇價錢"},{"pid":"c480f5a3e2827a45df85e69a059d01f1bb6cf524","tid":110101,"uid":62650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T12:44:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日日番工搭的士</blockquote><br />\n其實呢樣我份工唔係唔得。但唔想咁做"},{"pid":"dc232f9ded0b77438d2ad4fb90b397bc22a0bd3f","tid":110101,"uid":4548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT